          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Constitutional Amendment</strong></p> <p>This joint resolution proposes a constitutional amendment denying the President the power to grant himself a reprieve or pardon for an offense against the United States.</p>]]></text>
